data.title: Types of Financial Aid
data.text:
What financial aid is available?

We are dedicated to helping you navigate every single option that may help you pay for your Davenport education.

Employment

Davenport's Career Services department will help you research part-time jobs while you attend school.

Gift Aid

These are programs that are awarded based upon your past performance and/or need. You don't have to repay Gift Aid. Gift Aid includes:

Federal grants

State grants and scholarships

Davenport institutional scholarships

Davenport Foundation scholarships

External scholarships

Athletic aid

Self-Help Aid
